  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1246">
<l>kalantuṇarntuṅ kātalark kaṇṭāṟ pulantuṇarāy </l>
<l>poykkāyvu kāytiyeṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O my soul! when you see the dear one who remove dislike by intercourse, you are displeased and continue to be so. Nay, your displeasure is (simply) false.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
